# Disaster Recovery (DR) & Business Continuity Plan â€“ Hospital IT

DR and BCP are mandatory for hospital operations.

## DR Objectives
- Protect patient data
- Ensure system availability
- Minimize downtime
- Enable safe clinical operations

## Key Components
- Data backup strategy (frequency, retention)
- Restore testing schedule
- Failover procedures
- Manual downtime workflows

## BCP Considerations
- Alternate registration process
- Manual billing fallback
- Communication protocols
- Post-incident review and improvement
